The U.S. Treasury said it will sell13.2 billion dlrs of three and six-month bills at its regularauction next week.    The June 8 sale, to be evenly divided between the three andsix month issues, would result in a paydown of 1.3 billion dlrsas maturing bills total 14.512 billion dlrs.    The bills are to be issued June 11. Reuter&#3;